latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Posted @withregram • @rockystarofficial Introducing Rocky Star Festive 2021 collection,the “Sprinkled Sartorial Bliss” a perfect blend of heritage times and modern cuts.
It is a special couture collection, where we are celebrating our brands signature embroideries and silhouettes by revisiting luxury with soft shapes and delicate workmanship. It is artistically interpreted through extravagant hand weaving craft. At Rocky Star house we are crafting a collection for a woman who inspires, rules and motivates.
The collection aims to reflect combination of fabrics like tulle and silk with soft, fresh and dusty colours. Served with whimsical flowers recalling the Victorian era, featuring handcrafted jewelled belts and neck pieces.
Bringing the old world charm, with our signature appliqué and thread work detailing.
